msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Flåde 🚚</span></strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Sell product sets 🔩</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Salg af produktsæt 🔩</span></strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A good work cannot be achieved without motivated and skilled employees, "
"reliable equipment nor suitable vehicles."
msgstr ""
"Uden motiverede og kvalificerede medarbejdere, pålideligt udstyr og egnede "
"køretøjer kan man ikke levere et godt stykke arbejde."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A link to reach the online quotation from where the customer can confirm and"
" sign it."
msgstr ""
"Et link til online-tilbuddet, hvor kunden kan bekræfte og underskrive det."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Accurately track the project 🔍"
msgstr "Følg projektet nøje 🔍"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All these components will give you an accurate overview on the project "
"profitability."
msgstr ""
"Alle disse komponenter giver dig et klart overblik over projektets "
"rentabilitet."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Amazing employees deserve amazing equipment. Make the sure all your tools are fit and well by tracking their health in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance</font></strong> app."
msgstr ""
"Fantastiske medarbejdere fortjener fantastisk udstyr. Sørg for, at alt "
"værktøj er klar til brug ved hjælp af\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Vedligeholdelsesappen</"
"font></strong>."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Analytic Items ➡️ Track any cost using Analytic Items from the Accounting "
"App"
msgstr ""
"Analyseposter ➡️ Hold styr på alle omkostninger med analyseposter i "
"Bogføringsappen"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Architect"
msgstr "Arkitekt"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As the first invoicing step, create a down payment from the sales order. This will generate the first invoice in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font></strong> app. Then, schedule one or several \"Invoicing Schedule\" activities on the sales order with the aim to never forget to send an intermediary invoice in order to sustain\n"
"            your cash flow."
msgstr ""
"Opret først en forskudsbetaling fra salgsordren. Dette genererer den første "
"faktura i\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Faktureringsappen</font></"
"strong>. Planlæg derefter en eller flere aktiviteter af typen "
"\"Faktureringsplan\" på salgsordren for at sikre, at ingen mellemfakturaer "
"overses, og at\n"
"            pengestrømmen forbliver stabil."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Assign the tasks to the right responsible and easily check the progress in "
"the Kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Tildel opgaverne til de rette personer, og følg nemt fremskridtet i Kanban-"
"visningen."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time, you can create from an opportunity a beautiful and tailor-made "
"quotation that displays the price, the discount, the unit of measure, and "
"the tax of each:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan til enhver tid oprette et attraktivt og skræddersyet tilbud ud fra en "
"salgsmulighed, hvor pris, rabat, måleenhed og moms fremgår for hver post:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "Det grundlæggende"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Before generating an intermediary invoice in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font></strong> app, freeze the project status in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project</font></strong> app to get an overview on the progress in terms of:"
msgstr ""
"Inden du opretter en mellemregning i            <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Faktureringsappen</font></strong>, skal du fastfryse projektstatus "
"i <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Projektappen</font></strong> for at "
"få et klart overblik over fremskridtet:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Before starting the project, make sure you have enough stock. The confirmation of the quotation also triggers the creation of a delivery in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory</font></strong>\n"
"            app where you can check the stock levels of each needed storable product."
msgstr ""
"Før du går i gang med projektet, skal du sikre dig, at der er tilstrækkeligt "
"lager. Bekræftelsen af tilbuddet udløser samtidig oprettelsen af en levering "
"i <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Lagerappen</font>,</strong>\n"
"            hvor du kan kontrollere lagerbeholdningen for hvert nødvendigt "
"lagervareprodukt."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Bills of Materials"
msgstr "Styklister"

#. module: construction
#: model:product.template,name:construction.product_product_5_product_template
msgid "Building Blocks 39x14x19cm"
msgstr "Byggeklodser 39 x 14 x 19 cm"

#. module: construction
#: model:project.task.type,name:construction.planning_project_stage_4
msgid "Cancelled"
msgstr "Annulleret"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Centralize all the important information 📝"
msgstr "Saml alle vigtige oplysninger ét sted 📝"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Construction"
msgstr "Konstruktion"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create an opportunity each time you face a potential customer, receive a "
"phone call, etc."
msgstr ""
"Opret en salgsmulighed, hver gang du møder en potentiel kunde, modtager et "
"opkald eller lignende."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Dashboard ➡️ Your project's status at a glance."
msgstr "Dashboard ➡️ Overblik over dit projekts status på et øjeblik."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "Vil du tage det et skridt videre?"

#. module: construction
#: model:project.task.type,name:construction.planning_project_stage_3
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Udført"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Down Payment"
msgstr "Acontobetaling"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During and after the construction project, provide a five star customer service by answering the questions from your customer through the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Helpdesk</font></strong> app. All the emails sent to"
msgstr ""
"Tilbyd 5-stjernet kundeservice under og efter byggeprojektet ved at besvare "
"kundernes spørgsmål og hjælpe dem via\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kundeserviceappen</font>"
".</strong> Alle e-mails sendt til"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Easily create beautiful quotations 💲"
msgstr "Nem oprettelse af smukke tilbud 💲"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Efficiently schedule the work 📆"
msgstr "Planlæg arbejdet effektivt 📆"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Enrich the core apps by installing the following ones."
msgstr "Udvid de primære apps ved at tilføje følgende apps."

#. module: construction
#: model:account.analytic.account,name:construction.account_analytic_account_2
msgid "Field Service"
msgstr "Udkørende service"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For each ordered material, don't forget to fill the analytic distribution in"
" which you will be able to set for which project it will be used."
msgstr ""
"Husk at udfylde omkostningsfordelingen for hvert bestilt materiale, så du "
"kan angive, hvilket projekt det skal anvendes til."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From WH ➡️ Deliveries from your warehouse to this specific construction site"
msgstr "Fra lager ➡️ Leverancer fra lager til byggeplads"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If a technical operation such as a repair is needed, directly create a task in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Field Service</font></strong> project from a ticket. Then assign it and schedule it to quickly solve the\n"
"            problem. Your employee will be able to use some material to fix the issue. Then these materials and the time spent could be invoiced to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er behov for teknisk assistance, f.eks. en reparation, kan du "
"oprette en opgave direkte fra en sag i projektet for <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Udkørende Service</font></strong>. Derefter kan "
"opgaven tildeles og planlægges, så\n"
"            problemet hurtigt kan løses. Din medarbejder kan bruge de "
"nødvendige materialer til at udføre arbejdet, og både materialer og den "
"anvendte tid kan efterfølgende faktureres til kunden."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If the customer replies to the email, the answer is automatically logged in the chatter on the right of the screen. Thereby, all the discussions regarding the quotation, its updates, and its fine tuning are attached, and the history\n"
"            can be easily consulted by all the involved users"
msgstr ""
"Når kunden svarer på e-mailen, logges svaret automatisk i chatten til højre "
"på skærmen. På den måde vedhæftes alle diskussioner om tilbuddet, dets "
"opdateringer og finjusteringer, og forløbet\n"
"            kan nemt følges af alle involverede brugere"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If the stock levels are too low, resupply the materials from the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase</font></strong> app by creating a purchase order linked to the right vendor. In the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Contact</font></strong> app, you can easily manage all your\n"
"            preferred vendors and don't hesitate to set a warning to remind if there is a minimum amount to get free transport costs."
msgstr ""
"Hvis lagerbeholdningen er for lav, kan du genbestille materialerne via\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Indkøbsappen</font></"
"strong> ved at oprette en ordre til den relevante leverandør. I <strong>"
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kontakterappen</font></strong> kan du nemt "
"administrere alle dine foretrukne leverandører og oprette en advarsel, der "
"minder dig\n"
"            om minimumsordrer for at reducere transportomkostningerne."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to push your quotation building much further and add all the "
"power of Spreadsheet beneath any line of your Sales Orders, use the quote "
"calculation feature."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil tage udarbejdelsen af tilbud et skridt videre og indsætte "
"regnearkets beregninger under hver ordrelinje, skal du bruge "
"tilbudsberegningsfunktionen."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If your country benefits from a tax rebate under certain conditions, you can"
" easily apply it to your entire quotation by creating a fiscal position that"
" will automatically replace the default tax rate by the reduced one"
msgstr ""
"Hvis dit land under visse betingelser har ret til en skattelettelse, kan du "
"nemt anvende den på hele tilbuddet ved at oprette en skattepost, som "
"automatisk erstatter standardskattesatsen med den nedsatte"

#. module: construction
#: model:project.task.type,name:construction.planning_project_stage_2
msgid "In Progress"
msgstr "Behandles"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Increase you visibility and get more leads by creating a beautiful\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website</font></strong>! When a potential customer sends a request through the contact form, it could automatically create an opportunity in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM</font></strong> app."
msgstr ""
"Øg din synlighed, og få flere leads ved at oprette en attraktiv\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">hjemmeside</font></strong>"
"! Når en potentiel kunde sender en forespørgsel via kontaktformularen, kan "
"der automatisk oprettes en salgsmulighed i\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM-</font></strong>appen."

