msgid ""
"Record the time spent by your employees on each project by using the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Timesheets</font></strong> app. Don't forget to define a hourly cost on the employee form."
msgstr ""
"Registrér den tid, dine medarbejdere har brugt på hvert projekt, via\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Tidsregistreringerappen</"
"font></strong>. Husk at angive en timesats på medarbejderformularen."

