#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Save time by directly sending the quotation by email to your customer. The "
"personalized email provides:"
msgstr ""
"Spar tid ved at sende tilbuddet direkte til kunden via e-mail. Den "
"personlige e-mail indeholder:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Schedule a demo"
msgstr "Planlæg en demo"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Service such as labor hours, traveling costs, etc."
msgstr "Tjenesteydelser såsom arbejdstid, rejseudgifter osv."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Speed up the signing process thanks to the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Sign</font></strong> app. Once again, all the signed documents will be stored in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Documents</font></strong> app."
msgstr ""
"Fremskynd underskriftsprocessen med\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">e-Signaturappen</font></"
"strong>. Alle underskrevne dokumenter gemmes også automatisk i <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Dokumenterappen</font></strong>."

#. module: construction
#: model:product.template,description_sale:construction.product_product_5_product_template
msgid ""
"Standard gray concrete block, hollow, 39x14x19 cm, for all load-bearing and "
"non-load-bearing masonry, indoors and outdoors. This concrete block meets "
"the strict quality requirements of the BENOR label."
msgstr ""
"Grå standardbetonsten, hul, 39×14×19 cm, til alle bærende og ikke-bærende "
"murværker, både indendørs og udendørs. Betonstenen opfylder de strenge "
"kvalitetskrav for BENOR-mærket."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Starting a construction project implies a lot of important documents such as contracts, building plans, instructions for use, subcontracting agreements, etc. Instead of scattering them in your emails, storage services or computer,\n"
"            attach them in the chatter and they will be automatically centralized in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Documents</font></strong> app."
msgstr ""
"For at starte et byggeprojekt kræves mange vigtige dokumenter, f.eks. "
"kontrakter, byggeplaner, brugsanvisninger og aftaler med underleverandører. "
"I stedet for at sprede dem i e-mails, på lagringstjenester eller på din "
"computer,\n"
"            kan du blot vedhæfte dem i chatteren, så de automatisk samles i\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Dokumenterappen</font></"
"strong>."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take advantage of every opportunity. The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM</font></strong> centralizes everything and allows you to ensure the follow-up of each request efficiently. If the request becomes concrete, create the\n"
"            customer in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Contact</font></strong> app."
msgstr ""
"Udnyt alle salgsmuligheder. <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM-"
"appen</font></strong> samler alt og sikrer, at alle henvendelser bliver "
"fulgt op. Når henvendelsen bliver konkret, kan du oprette\n"
"            kunden i <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kontakterappen</"
"font></strong>."

#. module: construction
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:construction.project_project_1
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:construction.project_project_3
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:construction.project_project_4
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "Opgaver"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Thanks to the invoicing policy set on delivered quantities, the generated "
"invoice is always the reflect of the reality on the field and it is fair for"
" the customer."
msgstr ""
"Takket være afregningspolitikken, som er baseret på de leverede mængder, "
"afspejler den udarbejdede faktura altid det faktiske forbrug på stedet og "
"sikrer en fair behandling af kunden."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> <strong>CRM</strong> </font> application"
" allows you to collect requests from your potential customers by aggregating"
" several sources:"
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> <strong>CRM-appen</strong> </font> giver dig "
"mulighed for at samle henvendelser fra potentielle kunder fra flere "
"forskellige kanaler:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "The customer reminders."
msgstr "Kundepåmindelser."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "The financial reporting."
msgstr "Finansiel rapportering."

#. module: construction
#: model:product.template,description_sale:construction.product_product_6_product_template
msgid ""
"The prepared mortar is a dry, industrially premixed masonry mortar in "
"strength class M5. The mortar is mainly designed for load-bearing and non-"
"load-bearing masonry."
msgstr ""
"Den færdigblandede mørtel er en tør, industrielt forblandet murmørtel i "
"styrkeklasse M5, primært beregnet til både bærende og ikke-bærende murværk."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The quotation confirmation automatically triggers the creation of a "
"dedicated project in the... <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Project</font></strong> app! Each project is initiated with "
"several default tasks, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Når tilbuddet bekræftes, oprettes der automatisk et særskilt projekt i "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Projektappen</font></strong>! Hvert "
"projekt indeholder nogle standardopgaver, såsom:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "The quotation in PDF format"
msgstr "Tilbuddet i PDF-format"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "The synchronisation with the banks."
msgstr "Synkroniseringen med bankerne."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "The vendor bills payment."
msgstr "Betaling af leverandørfakturaer."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This industry is tailor-made for construction businesses that excel in managing construction projects. It encompasses the crucial stages of project conceptualization, accurate quotation(s), seamless project kick-off, meticulous\n"
"            planning, streamlined (re)supply, flawless execution, effective collaboration with third parties, meticulous budget follow-up, prompt invoicing, and exceptional customer service."
msgstr ""
"Denne brancheløsning er skræddersyet til byggefirmaer, der udmærker sig i "
"effektiv projektledelse. Den dækker alle væsentlige faser i "
"projektudformning, herunder præcise omkostningsoverslag, problemfri "
"projektstart, grundig\n"
"            planlægning, optimeret indkøb, fejlfri udførelse, effektivt "
"samarbejde med tredjeparter, nøje budgetkontrol, hurtig fakturering og "
"fremragende kundeservice."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Time spent on the project."
msgstr "Tid brugt på projektet."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Timesheets"
msgstr "Tidsregistreringer"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "To WH ➡️ Products sent back to your warehouse"
msgstr "Til lageret ➡️ Produkter returneret til dit lager"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To ease the quotation of usually sold together, the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Manufacturing</font></strong> app allows you to create kits. These can contain several products. When added in a quotation, the kits is displayed as a single line but the delivery order displays\n"
"            all the components to pick up."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre det lettere at oprette tilbud på produkter, der ofte sælges "
"sammen, kan du bruge\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Produktionsappen</font></"
"strong> til at oprette sæt. Et sæt kan indeholde flere produkter. Når sættet "
"føjes til et tilbud, vises det som en enkelt linje, mens leveringsordren "
"viser\n"
"            alle de enkelte komponenter, der skal leveres."

#. module: construction
#: model:product.template,name:construction.product_product_7_product_template
msgid "Travelling costs"
msgstr "Rejseudgifter"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting</font></strong> "
"app to easily handle:"
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Bogføringsappen</font></strong> "
"til nemt at administrere:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning</font></strong> app to organize the work of your employees. Define on which project and when they have to work. Easily manage shift conflicts, workload and replacements in case\n"
"            of leaves."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planlægningsappen</font></"
"strong> til at organisere dine medarbejderes arbejde. Angiv, hvilket projekt "
"de skal arbejde på, og hvornår. Administrér nemt vagtoverskridelser, "
"arbejdsbyrde og vikarer ved\n"
"            fravær."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the Website app to create a contact form that will redirect all the "
"requests to the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Brug Hjemmesideappen til at oprette en kontaktformular, der sender alle "
"forespørgsler direkte til <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM</font></"
"strong>."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:construction.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Velkommen! God fornøjelse med at gå på opdagelse."

